These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, musical
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, turquise
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, mexican
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bike
1. the person who likes turquise is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
2. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Movie-Genre      | musical      | superhero    |
| Color           | turquise | mauve |
| Nationality   | italian       | mexican  |
| Transport     | airplane      | bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, blue
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, scooter
1. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | watermelon | cauliflower |
| Flower   | lily       | orchid         |
| Color           | blue     | red         |
| Transport     | scooter    | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
City: hamburg, marseilles
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, r&b
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
4. the person playing poker is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking          | board-games |
| City           | marseilles | hamburg     |
| Music-Genre   | folk            | r&b         |
| Game     | poker         | mah-jongg   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, amber
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, trance
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: july, june
1. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
2. the person drinking tea is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | tea     | cola   |
| Color   | amber    | red |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | trance |
| Birthday           | july | june    |

